{"tid":18352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林祖舜,害死你既唔係連尼住同高登仔,害你既你蕭若元!!","createTime":"2016-12-02T08:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T08:56:14.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d64d2631e882d44d9bce14996b19462d8bd7c3b","tid":18352,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:49:37.000Z","msg":"香港人網提出併購高登事件發生於2011年7月18日，創辦香港人網的蕭若元，在新浪微博中宣佈，表示將收購香港最具人氣的高登討論區。有關消息傳出之後，隨即群情洶湧，不少網民均表示反對，有人甚至以「反對新媒體霸權」號召抗爭，在facebook開設專頁聯署反對香港人網的併購行動。<br />\n<br />\n是次事件於2011年7月19日被多份報章報導。<br />\n<br />\n燈力潛伏期長達5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林祖舜你要尋仇自己找蕭若元吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b47b9424abd64fbc150d114114cc3f78dc9a3df","tid":18352,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4527bc65a6aee878efbfdcb0d7a8b49cdd318a","tid":18352,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:56:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}